title: Demand Deposits, Individuals, Corporations, and Others, Weekly Reporting Member Banks for New York, NY
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Four Variables--(1)--Orignal Data, 1919-1934 (2)--Original Data, 1934-1939 (3)--Original Data, 1939-1947 (4)--Original Data, 1946-1949. Data Exclude Demand Deposits Of States And Political Subdivisions. Source: Federal Reserve Board, Data For 1939-1941: Banking And Monetary Statistics, 1943. Data For 1942-1947: Federal Reserve Bulletin, Monthly.
